219
00:20:32,732 --> 00:20:35,651
If you get it for me
I'll do anything for you.

220
00:20:35,818 --> 00:20:37,695
The muskrat...

221
00:20:37,862 --> 00:20:40,906
Yeah?
Swipe that notebook then!

222
00:20:42,658 --> 00:20:44,618
Okay.

223
00:20:45,286 --> 00:20:47,621
